22
00:01:27,460 --> 00:01:30,200
For people who turn up in the morning—you flip a coin.

23
00:01:30,200 --> 00:01:34,910
If they get heads, they go to one film—tails, they go to the other film.

24
00:01:34,910 --> 00:01:38,600
People who show up in the afternoon, you do the same thing.

25
00:01:38,600 --> 00:01:42,090
That way, you&#39;re going to have roughly an equal number of people with different levels

26
00:01:42,090 --> 00:01:45,780
of base level arousal in both film conditions.

27
00:01:45,780 --> 00:01:50,120
Then it can&#39;t be due to individual differences, like anxiety.

28
00:01:50,120 --> 00:01:54,500
We also would call this type of alternate explanation a confounding variable.

29
00:01:54,500 --> 00:01:59,740
