30
00:01:59,740 --> 00:02:04,460
that makes it difficult to work out what the effect of the independent variable is.

31
00:02:04,460 --> 00:02:09,040
In the initial version of the film experiment I described, the confounding variable—you

32
00:02:09,039 --> 00:02:13,510
