41
00:02:50,250 --> 00:02:54,909
We&#39;d have to do that really unethical and illegal experiment that I described to disentangle

42
00:02:54,909 --> 00:02:56,560
these things.

43
00:02:56,560 --> 00:03:00,661
Third variables can make it difficult to tease apart cause-and-effect relationships, and

44
00:03:00,661 --> 00:03:02,430
so we use random assignment.

